# Go Calculator API

REST API калькулятора на Go.

## Stack

- Go
- Echo
- GORM
- SQLite
- Docker
- Govaluate

## Endpoints

GET /calculations  
POST /calculations  
PATCH /calculations/:id  
DELETE /calculations/:id  

## Example request

POST /calculations

{
  "expression": "2+2*5"
}

Response

{
  "id": "...",
  "expression": "2+2*5",
  "result": "12"
}

## Run

go run ./cmd
